        <updateDate>2021-07-07T21:27:21Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>World Bank Integrity Preservation Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the U.S. Executive Director of the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development to oppose any extension of financial or technical assistance by the bank to a country that both exceeds the graduation threshold of the bank and is designated as a country of particular concern for religious freedom.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
